an_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a division\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"the big names\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"Team SA\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 320}, {\"ngram\": \"three initial squads\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wayde van Niekerkis a household name in South Africa.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999998772182, \"rank\": 1.2285523576334496e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wayde van Niekerkis\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"a household name\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been ever since winning the Olympic 400m gold in world-record time atRio 2016.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic 400m gold\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"world-record time\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Running in lane eight, Van Niekerk crossed the line in 43.03 seconds, claiming a world record previously held since 1999 by the sport's greatMichael Johnson.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.6069010122837932, \"rank\": 0.6423683435550054, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lane\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"43.03 seconds\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Increasingly, there appear to be positive signs of Van Niekerk rediscovering his best form after an injury-plagued period in his career, which began with a freak accident in 2017 when he he tore his anterior cruciate ligament and meniscus cartilage during a charity touch rugby match at Newlands.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newlands_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9842563428480111, \"rank\": 0.01599548457717234, \"text\": \"Newlands\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newlands_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newlands_Stadium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"positive signs\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"his best form\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury-plagued period\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"a freak accident\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"his anterior cruciate ligament\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"meniscus cartilage\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"a charity touch rugby match\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully that isall behind him, though, as he recently posted an Olympic qualifying time of 44.08 seconds at the 2023 Silesia Diamond League meeting in Poland.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silesia\", \"score\": 0.9960854445478515, \"rank\": 0.003915377268716698, \"text\": \"Silesia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silesia\"}, {\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0936931537128247e-13, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9205882595614981, \"rank\": 0.08624795464584398, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hopefully that isall\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic qualifying time\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"44.08 seconds\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we think of any athlete who had a crazy, unexpected injury, most likely do not make finals and do not challenge for races,\\\" Van Niekerk said on theBehind the Ruck Podcast.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any athlete\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"a crazy, unexpected injury\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"theBehind\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ruck Podcast\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is about being kinder with yourself again, allowing yourself to be exposed to that environment again, and start believing you are a champion again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\